==Japanese==
{{ja-kanjitab|見}}

===Verb===
{{ja-verb|kk|type=2|hira=みる|rom=miru}}

# to [[see]], to [[watch]], to [[observe]], to [[look]] at something
# to [[look over]], to [[examine]], to [[judge]]
# to [[take care of]], to [[look after]], to [[keep an eye on]] somebody
# to [[view]] something, like [[painting]]s, [[flower]]s or a [[movie]]
# {{context|usually after the {{term||-て form|-[[te form]]}} of a verb}} to [[try]]

====Related terms====
*[[見える]] ([[みえる]], [[mieru]])
*[[診る]] ([[みる]], [[miru]])
*[[看る]]

====Synonyms====
*[[視聴する]] ([[しちょうする]], [[shichōsuru]]): [[watch]] and [[listen]] (to [[TV]] or [[video]])

====Derived terms====
*[[見せる]] ([[みせる]], ''miseru'')
*[[見る影もない]], [[見る影も無い]] ([[みるかげもない]], [[mirukagemonai]]): mere shadow of one's former self; having no trace left of something great once possessed
*[[夢を見る]] ([[ゆめをみる]], [[yume o miru]])

